Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:21.66,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:17705,21668}Whenever my feelings were hurt,\NI couldn't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:25.58,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:21668,25588}because I held a lie in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:29.55,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25588,29551}Time moved faster than I could react,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:34.59,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29551,34597}so I pulled myself away\Nfrom everything, but now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.64,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:34597,40645}I can't stop anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:47.61,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:41062,47610}Accepting everything, I rise up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:53.49,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:49571,53491}I'll fly over all of time\Nwhile holding onto your presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.99,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:53491,56995}following the trace of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:03.00,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56995,63001}My world becomes engulfed with light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:09.25,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:65461,69257}A never ending sky,\Nyour never changing eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:12.96,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:69257,72969}I want to love these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:19.35,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:72969,79350}No matter the distance,\Nor if we are separated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:22.77,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:79350,82770}we are always connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:29.44,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:87066,89444}Want you here tonight!
Comment: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:31.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:91112,91112}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:50.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:107295,110006}We haven't dined out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:53.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110381,113885}Let's make the best of it\Nby eating something great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:56.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113885,116471}But there's a long line everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:58.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116721,118931}Leave it to me! I know a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121267,122894}Well, here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.26,0:02:06.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123269,126064}Tsujimoto Mansion? It looks pricey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126064,129359}– Don't worry. Father's paying.\N– What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.28,0:02:18.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137283,138993}Are you sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:24.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139452,144457}I came here a few years ago.\NTheir rice gruel is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:27.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144957,147418}Reasonable prices, nice owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:30.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147919,150880}But something's strange.\NDid they redecorate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:38.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154092,158805}I'm sorry, but we don't take\Ncustomers without reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:43.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159138,163893}I don't remember needing one.\NIsn't the chef Mr. Tsujimoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:47.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163893,167730}That is correct,\Nbut the owner has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:52.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168523,172235}I'm Ookura, the owner. Is there\Nsomething I can do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:55.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172777,175571}Is it true you need\Na reservation to eat here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:03:02.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176030,182036}We only prepare meals for\Nthree groups of customers per day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182578,184997}So we refuse those\Nwith no reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184997,187250}That's why there's no line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:12.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187834,192714}If you want to eat here, please make\Na reservation and come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192964,194716}And when would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195091,197385}Probably about three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197385,199137}Three years?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199929,201347}We look forward to your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205017,207645}That owner has such a rude attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:33.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207645,213568}Some cuisine critic must have praised\Nthem and it's gone to their heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213568,215236}Well, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218865,221200}Let's get ahold of our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.33,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:228082,230334}Steal the Chinese Iron Chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:54.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233504,234630}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235006,238050}That place has the greatest sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238050,239510}It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239510,240219}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:04.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240762,244432}A new octopus fritter shop\Nnear the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:09.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244432,249145}We're discussing whether that one\Nor the one near the park is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:13.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249687,253566}– What do you think?\N– Maybe the one near the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:18.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254066,258404}See, I told you! That's a taste\Nthat's hard to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258404,260907}Hey, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:24.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260907,264494}Let's stop by there after\Nschool for a small snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264911,268206}How can you talk about that\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:31.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268206,271000}Something's wrong\Nwith your stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270958,272126}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:37.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272335,277298}Aren't I right? You're all going\Nto end up with faces like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:42.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277882,282345}How rude! And you're taking\Nforever to catch St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282345,283805}Now you've said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283805,286682}You don't know\Nif they're friends or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295566,297568}Wasn't that Miss Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:03.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297944,303950}Yes. She came to ask us\Nfor help with her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:08.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303950,308996}Her grandmother has been in the\Nhospital for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:13.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309622,313793}Lately she's lost her appetite\Nand can't get out of bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:18.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313793,318339}Feeling sorry for her, Miss Sato\Nasked what she wanted to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318548,322552}There was something she wanted\Nto eat again while she was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:26.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323261,326514}– What could it be?\N– Rice gruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.51,0:05:27.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326514,327765}Rice gruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327765,328683}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:32.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328683,332103}It's an unforgettable dish\Nan old boyfriend made.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:36.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332103,336357}The story goes back to when\Nthe grandmother was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:40.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336357,340194}She fell in love with a young chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340194,342905}But they were destined\Nto be torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:48.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343406,348369}{\i1}Goodbye. My parents have decided\Non a fiance I am to wed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350121,351497}Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351998,353457}Ajinosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353457,355501}Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356961,358462}Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358880,360923}Ajinosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:03.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361299,363384}Chiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:16.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371058,376063}That was the last time she saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:22.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378190,382528}Recently she found out that\Nhe became a famous chef
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382528,385489}and opened a restaurant here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:29.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385489,389702}But the grandmother is in no\Ncondition to leave the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:33.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389702,393831}For her sake Miss Sato\Nkept going to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:36.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394081,396542}But she hasn't been\Nable to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:38.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396876,398502}That's just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398794,402465}No, the one who 's terrible\Nis the restaurant owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:46.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403090,406928}Business has been bad\Nsince the new owner took it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407178,410890}He's gone against every\Nwish the chef has.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:54.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410890,414560}He's even made sure that this story\Nhasn't reached the chef's ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:415728,417855}Do you mean Tsujimoto Mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:03.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418272,423736}That's right. The chef is Ajinosuke\NTsujimoto, the Chinese Iron Chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424278,426948}But how do you know\Nof the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427198,428824}Just a tiny incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:12.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428824,432411}The grandmother's wish is\Nto eat his cooking, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432954,435289}She really wants to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:18.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435289,438376}Leave it to me!\NSt. Tail will make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:30.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444632,450721}Those girls only think about eating.\NThey have no sex appeal. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453557,455768}Asuka, let's stop here before we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455768,457144}Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:39.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457144,459981}Look! It's a message from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459981,461232}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:48.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463943,468572}"Tonight I will be stealing\Nthe Chinese Iron Chef. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:53.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469156,473202}Didn't think St. Tail was\Na gourmet fan, did you, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473202,475746}Sorry, guys. See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487049,490553}You're saying that St. Tail's\Ngoing to steal the chef?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:13.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490553,493139}Well, that is a great honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:17.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493139,497351}Don't joke. You will cooperate\Nwith us in her arrest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:21.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497768,501564}Yes, most certainly.\NLet me introduce you. Tsujimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:26.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502064,506485}This is the Chinese Iron Chef\Nhimself, Ajinosuke Tsujimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506777,509780}This is Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509780,513451}A pleasure. I am guarding you\Nfrom St. Tail today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513868,515244}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:38.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515494,518164}Yes. Tonight, please do as I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523419,525087}A master chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:55.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534180,535014}You little goof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:06.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545191,546150}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548694,550321}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551822,552948}Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552948,554867}Your name is Asuka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:15.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554867,555576}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555576,558287}Is St. Tail really going\Nto capture me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:23.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:558704,563250}Yes, but there's nothing to worry\Nabout. I'm going to get her for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567546,569215}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592154,595199}Dad! What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595199,597159}That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:59.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597159,599453}I came after St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599453,601747}St. Tail is coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:02.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601747,602414}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:05.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602414,605417}– That's not good.\N– What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606001,609880}– You know of the Washington Treaty?\N– Washington Treaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.54,0:10:17.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610548,617429}Oh, it's to protect animals like koalas\Nand pandas from bad hunters, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:23.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617429,623269}It forbids buying and selling protected\Nanimals and punishes poachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:28.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623269,628691}Right. And the owner of this\Nrestaurant is breaking the treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629191,632653}They're running a black market\Nof protected animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633028,634613}A black market?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634613,636657}Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636657,638868}Did you get the evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:42.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639660,642955}Can't you tell by looking\Nat this outfit? Kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642955,644832}Why'd I have to meet you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:48.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644957,648919}If you've got a problem,\Ntell it to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648919,650796}Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652047,654592}Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:56.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654592,656051}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:00.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657970,660389}{\i1}Dad, I'll remember this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:03.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661015,663017}It's nothing.
Comment: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:09.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:669690,669690}Eyecatch A
Comment: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:15.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:675696,675696}Eyecatch B
Comment: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:20.70,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:680701,680701}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684121,686207}Meimi isn't coming down?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686207,688626}She's got a ton of homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:32.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689043,692588}I was going to teach Meimi\Nsome card tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:37.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693088,697551}No, you don't. You're trying to get\NMeimi to take after you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:42.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697968,702014}What's wrong with that?\NShe has talented hands, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702223,704975}What? She got her talent from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:49.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705309,709188}As usual, they're getting along fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714360,717363}Ruby, be a good girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728082,731877}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:17.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736924,737883}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:21.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740469,741553}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743597,745349}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:44.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759405,764285}Be careful. There are many other\Nbad rumors about Tsujimoto Mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765077,766495}Don't worry, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:52.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768664,772418}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:20.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796025,800237}– What's with all the police?\N– St. Tail is supposed to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800237,803949}St. Tail? Then I take it\Nthat the today's deal is off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.53,0:13:27.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804533,807369}Don't worry.\NHer target is the chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:32.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807369,812291}And don't you think a racket\Nlike that is to our advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812291,814084}Hurry and sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817296,818297}Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818297,820174}Today's customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820174,821258}Are there others?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821258,822593}This is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823344,826805}Then please close the shutters\Nuntil the meal ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859755,861840}I thought so. Just chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866178,869264}Please enjoy this evening's feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872142,873936}What's this? A blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:38.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874228,878023}– Turn the lights on!\N– I can't! They won't go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:42.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878440,882403}{\i1}The dinner will be put off\Nfor another day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882403,884446}Where are you, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885614,888409}Chef, don't let go of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891203,892413}That's the chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:05.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900212,905175}It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924611,926447}What are these things?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:30.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926989,930409}Chef! Take refuge in\Nthe storage room! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933162,934496}You won't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937624,938917}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940669,942880}That's far enough, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:46.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943255,946633}You thought you cornered me,\Nbut now I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:51.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946633,951054}Imagine catching St. Tail in\Na place like this! What luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:05.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961565,965194}One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983837,985047}Are the animals all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987674,990969}The animals—\NI mean, is the chef all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.59,0:16:34.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991595,994681}The chef is fine as of now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994932,997643}"I'll be taking\Nthe Iron Chef. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:39.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998185,999728}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:50.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005734,1010364}This is a baby bald eagle\Nillegally imported into Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:56.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015661,1016828}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019915,1021959}A lesser panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:09.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024711,1029424}That was wise of you to camouflage\Nthese protected animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029591,1031385}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032886,1035597}Cut the act.\NYou're under arrest, Ookura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043855,1045774}What will you do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046525,1049778}– It's not me who wants to see you.\N– Then who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:38.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054908,1058954}Your girlfriend from 50 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070215,1072217}This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104082,1105334}Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113300,1116720}It's the same taste as\N50 years ago, Ajinosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117304,1118972}Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:44.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119473,1124853}It's as if it were only yesterday.\NThe first time I met you, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133320,1136365}Excuse me.\NWill you dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137616,1138909}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:21.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156259,1161390}Did you see today's paper? The animals\Nwere returned to their homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161765,1165352}And Ookura and the others\Nwere arrested. Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:30.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165686,1170565}I wonder what happened to the chef.\NTsujimoto Mansion was closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170857,1172234}Are you interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172234,1173568}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:38.03,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1175570,1178031}Chinese Food: Shanghai Tei
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178990,1182703}Seira, I'm really not\Nin the mood for noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182703,1185247}Isn't it Meimi and Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185664,1188959}– Asuka Jr.!\N– I was thinking of having a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188959,1192713}I know the owner here.\NAre you two going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193338,1196633}I'll be passing this one up.\NSee you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.63,0:19:58.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196633,1198677}– Seira…\N– How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206059,1209104}Welcome! Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:13.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209563,1213316}– What does that mean?\N– Is this a date with your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213567,1215527}No, it's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:20.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215944,1220699}It's empty as usual. At this rate,\Nyou'll close down in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:24.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1220699,1224703}Maybe I'll advertise around\Ntown for you. The owner is—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:26.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224703,1226705}Don't you think\Nof uttering one more word!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:28.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227247,1228832}Yes. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230208,1231668}That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:34.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234004,1234921}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235213,1238592}Eat! The rice gruel here is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:48.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244181,1248059}– Delicious!\N– Didn't I tell you? Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248518,1250437}Hot!
